stories.text:
We've released v0.8.0 of our open-source access management tool Leapp (https://github.com/Noovolari/leapp).

You can now configure multiple AWS SSO endpoints and automatically import in Leapp all access methods. Here's a quick demo video: https://youtu.be/w1N7-anwmSo.

I would love to know your thoughts and feedbacks.
